io.mpos.provider
Interface ProviderWithServerSubsystem

All Superinterfaces:
Provider
public interface ProviderWithServerSubsystem
extends Provider

Provider additions, exposing some functions that should normally be handled by a server. Added for rapid prototyping and test scenarios.

Method Detail

registerTransactionWithTemplate

void registerTransactionWithTemplate(TransactionTemplate transactionTemplate)
                                     throws MposRuntimeException
Creates a new transaction that can then be used to complete a transaction. This step is normally done via a direct server-to-server call but here it is exposed for testing and rapid prototyping applications.

Parameters:
transactionTemplate - The template to use to create the transaction
Throws:
MposRuntimeException - If the parameters are invalid
Since:
2.0.0
